  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc7\u0bb7\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0b8e\u0bae\u0bcd.\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Senior MPs of Sajith's party get ministerial post",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "There are reports that five senior MPs of United People's Shakti are to be appointed as Cabinet Ministers.",
        "They have held powerful ministerial positions in the good governance government and will join the cabinet by accepting the invitation given by President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "The government is currently preparing to replace the multi-party government with a national government with the consensus of all parties.",
        "According to this, the MPs of several parties are going to jointly get ministerial posts as individual MPs, not parties.",
        "The news also mentioned that the new cabinet will be sworn in in a few days. (R)"
      ],
